&lt;p&gt;3) Tools - this is how the agent actually does things. Here, &lt;code&gt;finalize()&lt;/code&gt; signals completion.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight js-code-highlight"&gt;
&lt;pre class="highlight python"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="nd"&gt;@tool&lt;/span&gt;
