&lt;h3&gt;


Step 4: Building Key Components
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I'm only covering the core logic behind each component since the overall code is huge. You can find all the components in the repository at &lt;a href="https://github.com/CopilotKit/deep-agents-demo/tree/main/src/components" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;&lt;code&gt;src/components&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;âœ… ToolCard Component&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

