&lt;p&gt;Here's a brief explanation:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;useEffect&lt;/code&gt; registers the &lt;code&gt;Escape&lt;/code&gt; listener and locks body scroll only when a file is open, and cleans both up on close.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
