&lt;h3&gt;


Step 3: Expose the Agent via FastAPI + AG-UI
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The last step is to wire everything together and expose it as a FastAPI app. The &lt;code&gt;main.py&lt;/code&gt; builds the agent graph, configures which tool calls to emit to the frontend and registers the AG-UI endpoint.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight js-code-highlight"&gt;
&lt;pre class="highlight python"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="kn"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;os&lt;/span&gt;
